description: The file initializes and renders the main React application component 'App' into the DOM element with id 'root'. It sets up the root rendering context using ReactDOM and wraps the application in React.StrictMode for highlighting potential issues.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a React root for rendering React components into a DOM node.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders React elements into the React root, initiating the React rendering process.
